		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Network security</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Network security</b> consists of the provisions made in an underlying <a href="/wiki/Computer_network" title="Computer network">computer network</a> infrastructure, <a href="/wiki/Network_security_policy" title="Network security policy">policies</a> adopted by the <a href="/wiki/Network_administrator" title="Network administrator">network administrator</a> to protect the network and the network-accessible resources from <a href="/wiki/Authorization" title="Authorization">unauthorized</a> access, and consistent and continuous monitoring and measurement of its effectiveness (or lack) combined together.</p>
